        <main>
            <div class="about-container">
                <div class="about-header">
                    <h1>About Our Hospital Management System</h1>
                    <p>Transforming Healthcare Through Technology</p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-content">
                    <div class="about-section">
                        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                        <p>At HMS, our mission is to revolutionize healthcare management by providing cutting-edge
                            technology solutions that streamline operations, enhance patient care, and optimize resource
                            allocation. We believe in creating a healthcare ecosystem where administrative tasks are
                            simplified, allowing medical professionals to focus on what matters most—patient care.</p>

                        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                        <p>We envision a future where healthcare facilities operate with maximum efficiency, where
                            patient data is secure yet accessible to authorized personnel, and where the healthcare
                            journey is seamless for all stakeholders involved. Our goal is to be at the forefront of
                            digital transformation in healthcare administration.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="about-section">
                        <h2>Key Features</h2>
                        <ul class="feature-list">
                            <li>Intuitive patient registration and profile management</li>
                            <li>Advanced appointment scheduling system</li>
                            <li>Comprehensive electronic health records management</li>
                            <li>Real-time doctor availability tracking</li>
                            <li>Secure patient-doctor communication channels</li>
                            <li>Automated billing and insurance processing</li>
                            <li>Prescription management and pharmacy integration</li>
                            <li>Customizable reporting and analytics dashboard</li>
                            <li>Mobile-friendly interfaces for patients and staff</li>
                            <li>Role-based access control for enhanced security</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h2>Data Security & Compliance</h2>
                        <p>We understand the critical importance of healthcare data security. Our system implements
                            industry-leading encryption protocols, regular security audits, and strict access controls
                            to ensure compliance with international healthcare data protection standards. Your
                            information is always protected with us.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Journey</h2>
                    <div class="timeline">
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2020</div>
                            <p>HMS was conceptualized by a team of healthcare professionals and software engineers who
                                recognized the need for a more efficient hospital management solution.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2021</div>
                            <p>The first version of HMS was developed and piloted in three regional hospitals, receiving
                                valuable feedback from medical staff and administrators.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2022</div>
                            <p>HMS expanded its feature set and was implemented in over 50 healthcare facilities across
                                the country, serving more than 500,000 patients.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
                            <p>The platform underwent a major upgrade with enhanced security features and mobile app
                                integration for patients and doctors.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
                            <p>HMS received industry recognition with multiple awards for healthcare innovation and
                                expanded internationally.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2025</div>
                            <p>Today, HMS serves over 150 healthcare facilities worldwide with continuous development of
                                new features and capabilities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>By The Numbers</h2>
                    <div class="stats-container">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-number">150+</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Healthcare Facilities</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
